Exploratory plots of restoration activities in TB

library(tidyverse)
library(readxl)
library(ggmap)

fl <- 'data-raw/TBEP Restoration Database_11_21_07.xls'
dat <- fl %>% 
  read_excel %>% 
  select(Latitude, Longitude, Project_Completion_Date, Restoration_Technique, `Activity-1`, `Acres-1`) %>% 
  rename(
    lat = Latitude, 
    lon = Longitude, 
    date = Project_Completion_Date, 
    tech = Restoration_Technique, 
    type = `Activity-1`, 
    acre = `Acres-1`
  ) %>% 
  mutate(
    lat = as.numeric(lat),
    lon = as.numeric(lon),
    date = as.numeric(date)
  )
head(dat)
## # A tibble: 6 x 6
##        lat      lon  date                                     tech
##      <dbl>    <dbl> <dbl>                                    <chr>
## 1 27.48476 -82.3541  2000  Creatin of oyster habitat (oyster dome)
## 2 27.44120 -82.4312  2001 Creation of oyster habitat (oyster dome)
## 3 27.48341 -82.3556  2001  Creatin of oyster habitat (oyster dome)
## 4 27.55406 -82.3203  2001 Creation of oyster habitat (oyster dome)
## 5 27.43427 -82.4406  2002 Creation of oyster habitat (oyster dome)
## 6 27.47204 -82.3652  2002 Creation of oyster habitat (oyster dome)
## # ... with 2 more variables: type <chr>, acre <dbl>
ggplot(dat, aes(type, group = date, fill = factor(date))) + 
  geom_bar(position = 'dodge') + 
  theme_bw() + 
  theme(
    axis.title.x = element_blank(), 
    legend.title = element_blank()
    )

ggplot(dat, aes(acre, group = type, fill = type)) + 
  geom_histogram() + 
  scale_x_log10('Acres') + 
  facet_wrap(~type) + 
  theme_bw() + 
  theme(
    legend.position = 'none'
  )

toplo <- filter(dat, lat > 27.3 & lat < 28.2)  

# extent
ext <- make_bbox(toplo$lon, toplo$lat)
map <- get_stamenmap(ext, zoom = 11, maptype = "toner-lite")

# base map
pbase <- ggmap(map) +
  theme_bw() +
  theme(
    axis.title.x = element_blank(),
    axis.title.y = element_blank()
  ) +
  geom_point(data = toplo, aes(size = acre, fill = type), pch = 21, colour = 'black', alpha = 0.8) + 
  scale_size(range = c(2, 11))
pbase
